OL,3,C'Deeply alarming': MSP hits out at
OL,4,CScottish Government decision on NHS
OL,5,Cprojects
OL,7,FOn Monday the Scottish Government said
OL,8,Fit was suspending new building
OL,9,Fprojects due to financial pressures,
OL,10,Fand blamed the UK government in
OL,11,FWestminster, claiming its capital
OL,12,Finvestment budget had been cut in real
OL,13,Fterms due to rising inflation.
OL,15,F"The UK Government did not inflation-
OL,16,Fproof its capital budget which has
OL,17,Fresulted in nearly a 10% real-term cut
OL,18,Fin the Scottish Government's capital
OL,19,Ffunding over the medium-term between
OL,20,F2023-24 and 2027-28," a spokesperson
OL,21,Fsaid.
