OL,7,FOver a dozen projects have now been
OL,8,Fsuspended, none of which were planned
OL,9,Fto be in the . But Mr Hoy argued that
OL,10,Fthe policy made new infrastructure for
OL,11,Fthe local NHS less likely, saying this
OL,12,Fwould affect patients.
OL,14,F"Particularly in rural areas there is
OL,15,Fa need for investment in capital, and
OL,16,Fnew GP surgeries, and also in the
OL,17,FBorders General Hospital," he said.
OL,19,F"These cuts to the capital budget are
OL,20,Fdeeply alarming and distressing and
OL,21,Fwill impact patient care."
